{"id":18104,"date":"2022-12-31T04:32:39","date_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:32:39","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nd.wv3.net\/amg-car\/lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-sang-co-lon.html"},"modified":"2022-12-31T15:39:27","modified_gmt":"2022-12-31T15:39:27","slug":"lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-sang-co-lon","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/2022\/12\/31\/lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-sang-co-lon\/","title":{"rendered":"Lexus LX 600 \u2013 \u0110\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a m\u1edbi v\u1ec1 SUV h\u1ea1ng sang c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang.png\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-300x190.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-1024x649.png 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-768x487.png 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-1536x974.png 1536w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-600x380.png 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang.png 1920w\"><br><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_908_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang.png\" title=\"1672421524_908_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_908_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-300x69.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_908_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-600x138.png 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_908_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang.png 700w\"><\/p>\n<p>So v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u1ea7m h\u1ed1, t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a LX 570 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, LX 600 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lexus \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ea1i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n.  Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh kh\u1ed1i d\u1eadp n\u1ed5i c\u01a1 b\u1eafp gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay th\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng m\u1eb7t ph\u1eb3ng g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng v\u00e0 tinh gi\u1ea3n h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p>Theo \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Lexus, nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng lu\u00f4n thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y, LX600 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu xe th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch \u201cThe Next Chapter\u201d, h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1edf th\u00edch, nhu c\u1ea7u \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m m\u1edbi.  sang tr\u1ecdng r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t.<\/p>\n<p>Nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00ean m\u1eabu SUV \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Lexus ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh xu h\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0u ng\u00e0y nay, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb ph\u00f4 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m ri\u00eang t\u01b0.  \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n h\u00f3a. <\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_427_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang.png\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"1672421524_427_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_427_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-300x282.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_427_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-1024x961.png 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_427_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-768x721.png 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_427_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-1536x1442.png 1536w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_427_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-600x563.png 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_427_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang.png 1920w\"><\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t LX 600 n\u00e2ng ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf L-finesse l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi, t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 tinh t\u1ebf v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u01a1n.  L\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh con su\u1ed1t 3D v\u1edbi 7 thanh n\u1ed5i thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ba chi\u1ec1u, t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c li\u1ec1n m\u1ea1ch kh\u00f4ng vi\u1ec1n.  \u0110\u1ed9 d\u00e0y c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng thanh ngang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lexus tinh ch\u1ec9nh, ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eebng milimet gi\u00fap thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf tinh gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn t\u1ea1o \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ed7i khi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<p>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e8n LED 3 b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1eadn d\u1ea1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe Lexus.  \u0110\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb ban ng\u00e0y h\u00ecnh ch\u1eef L n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p d\u1ea1ng 3D, s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5u k\u00ednh t\u0103ng g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i so v\u1edbi phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea1o hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e2u theo t\u1eebng g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn.  T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 m\u1eabu xe \u0111i\u1ec7n UX, \u0111u\u00f4i xe LX m\u1edbi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee5m \u0111\u00e8n h\u1eadu LED n\u1ed1i li\u1ec1n, ch\u1eef Lexus t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u00ean \u0111u\u00f4i xe, thay cho logo truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng. <\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_853_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang.png\" title=\"1672421524_853_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_853_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-300x98.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_853_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-768x251.png 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_853_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-600x196.png 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_853_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang.png 883w\"><br><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_906_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang.png\" title=\"1672421524_906_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_906_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-300x98.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_906_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-600x195.png 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_906_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang.png 700w\"><\/p>\n<p>Ra m\u1eaft th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi, Lexus gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u.  \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, LX 600 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi ba phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n, d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng h\u1ea1ng sang v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 t\u00ednh kh\u00e1c nhau.<\/p>\n<p>Phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n cao c\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t LX 600 VIP c\u00f3 4 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ng\u1ed3i, h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf sau thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ki\u1ec3u doanh nh\u00e2n, d\u00e0nh cho nh\u1eefng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n \u01b0a th\u00edch tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i, tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 ti\u1ec7n nghi.  H\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t trang b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lexus t\u00edch h\u1ee3p tr\u00ean phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n n\u00e0y nh\u01b0: s\u01b0\u1edfi, l\u00e0m m\u00e1t, massage, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u1ea3 48 \u0111\u1ed9, m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh ri\u00eang t\u01b0, r\u00e8m che n\u1eafng, \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecdc s\u00e1ch\u2026 <\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_313_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang.png\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"1672421524_313_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_313_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-300x203.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_313_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-1024x691.png 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_313_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-768x518.png 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_313_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-1536x1037.png 1536w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_313_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-600x405.png 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421524_313_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang.png 1920w\"><\/p>\n<p>Gi\u00e1 \u1edf gi\u1eefa l\u00e0 LX 600 F Sport v\u1edbi trang b\u1ecb th\u1ec3 thao, h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n th\u1ec9nh tho\u1ea3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7m l\u00e1i v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m.  Phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb thanh \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, gi\u1ea3m x\u00f3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 sau, b\u1ed9 vi sai h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1ee3t Torsen gi\u00fap ph\u00e2n b\u1ed5 l\u1ef1c truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1i \u01b0u theo t\u1ea3i tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i m\u1ed7i b\u00e1nh xe.  Nh\u1eefng trang b\u1ecb n\u00e0y gi\u00fap t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1m \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u00e1i th\u1ec3 thao tr\u00ean phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n F-Sport.<\/p>\n<p>    \u201cNh\u1eefng hi\u1ec7u ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng l\u00e1i tr\u1ee3 l\u1ef1c \u0111i\u1ec7n EPS v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng treo th\u00edch \u1ee9ng AVS gi\u00fap t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng x\u1eed l\u00fd \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng th\u1ec3 thao thu\u1ea7n t\u00fay c\u1ee7a F Sport\u201d, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n h\u00e3ng cho bi\u1ebft.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421525_512_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang.png\" title=\"1672421525_512_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421525_512_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-300x268.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421525_512_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-1024x915.png 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421525_512_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-768x686.png 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421525_512_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-600x536.png 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421525_512_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang.png 1172w\"><\/p>\n<p>Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Urban v\u1edbi 7 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ng\u1ed3i.  C\u1ea3 ba phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u00e2m thanh 25 loa Mark Levinson, s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng loa l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe Lexus hi\u1ec7n nay.<\/p>\n<p>L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, m\u1eabu SUV c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Lexus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 V6, t\u0103ng \u00e1p k\u00e9p, dung t\u00edch 3,5 l\u00edt, c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 409 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn 650 Nm.  H\u1ed9p s\u1ed1 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng 10 c\u1ea5p.  C\u00e1c th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n LX 570 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat. <\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421525_289_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang.png\" title=\"1672421525_289_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421525_289_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-300x187.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421525_289_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-768x478.png 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421525_289_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-600x373.png 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421525_289_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang.png 892w\"><\/p>\n<p>Lexus trang b\u1ecb cho LX 600 nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 an to\u00e0n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac nh\u01b0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 kh\u1edfi h\u00e0nh ngang d\u1ed1c\/xu\u1ed1ng d\u1ed1c, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng an to\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc va ch\u1ea1m, c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o\/theo d\u00f5i l\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng\u2026 Xe c\u00f3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb 360- camera \u0111\u1ed9, 12 t\u00fai kh\u00ed \u1edf phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n VIP v\u00e0 10 t\u00fai kh\u00ed \u1edf hai phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n<p>N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a LX 600 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 gi\u1edbi si\u00eau gi\u00e0u \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u da v\u00e0 g\u1ed7 cao c\u1ea5p tr\u00e0n ng\u1eadp.  Bu\u1ed3ng l\u00e1i tr\u00ean LX m\u1edbi \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m Tazuna, cho ph\u00e9p ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i tr\u1ef1c quan h\u01a1n v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc xe.  M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh trung t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t nghi\u00eang 30 \u0111\u1ed9 theo h\u01b0\u1edbng xu\u1ed1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421525_751_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang.png\" title=\"1672421525_751_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421525_751_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-300x261.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421525_751_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang.png 433w\"><\/p>\n<p>H\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf sau c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u1eadp, ng\u1ea3, ch\u1ec9nh \u0111a v\u1ecb tr\u00ed.  Gh\u1ebf VIP tr\u00ean LX 600 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng gian th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n t\u1ed1i \u0111a v\u1edbi g\u00f3c ng\u1ea3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 48 \u0111\u1ed9, l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb NASA.  Kho\u1ea3ng s\u00e1ng g\u1ea7m xe c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh 4 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng treo th\u00edch \u1ee9ng AVS t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i b\u00ean trong cabin. <\/p>\n<p>\u00d4ng Takami Yokoo, k\u1ef9 s\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a d\u00f2ng LX m\u1edbi cho bi\u1ebft, h\u00e3ng t\u1ea1o ra phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n VIP nh\u1eb1m t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a kh\u00f4ng gian th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n cho doanh nh\u00e2n ngay c\u1ea3 khi ph\u1ea3i di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 n\u00e0y sang th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean nh\u1eefng cung \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng.  kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng ph\u1eb3ng.  Tri\u1ebft l\u00fd n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh trong ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 du\u1ed7i th\u1eb3ng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn tr\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7.<\/p>\n<p>T\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Lexus LX l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng xe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi doanh nh\u00e2n \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng b\u1edfi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng sang tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o, ti\u1ec7n nghi, tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9.  Lexus Vi\u1ec7t Nam hi\u1ec7n ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i 3 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n, gi\u00fap kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i v\u1ec1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea3m r\u1ee7i ro v\u1ec1 thu\u1ebf so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng.<\/p>\n<p>Ba phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a LX 600 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi g\u1ed3m: Urban 7 ch\u1ed7 gi\u00e1 8,1 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng;  F Sport 5 ch\u1ed7 gi\u00e1 8,35 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 VIP 4 ch\u1ed7 cao c\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t gi\u00e1 9,21 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng (\u0111\u00e3 bao g\u1ed3m VAT).<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421525_98_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang.png\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"1672421525_98_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421525_98_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-300x216.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421525_98_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-1024x737.png 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421525_98_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-768x552.png 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421525_98_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-1536x1105.png 1536w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421525_98_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang-600x432.png 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421525_98_lexus-lx-600-dinh-nghia-moi-ve-suv-hang.png 1920w\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">N\u1ed9i dung: Quang Anh \u2013 Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf: \u0110\u1ee9c Tr\u1ea7n \u2013 \u1ea2nh: Lexus Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n\t<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>So v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u1ea7m h\u1ed1, t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a LX 570 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, LX 600 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lexus \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ea1i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n. Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh kh\u1ed1i d\u1eadp n\u1ed5i c\u01a1 b\u1eafp gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay th\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng m\u1eb7t ph\u1eb3ng g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng v\u00e0 tinh gi\u1ea3n h\u01a1n. Theo \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Lexus, nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":17621,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[75],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18104"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=18104"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18104\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":18123,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18104\/revisions\/18123"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/17621"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=18104"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=18104"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=18104"}],"curies":[{"